PresentationTable.name: Orders Dates
PresentationTable.Description: -> This folder contains additional Orders Dates attributes like Order Date, Billed Date and so on.

PresentationColumn.name: Order Date
PresentationColumn.Description: Returns the Oder Date value from the Revenue Facts table. This field is of type Date.

PresentationColumn.name: Order Month
PresentationColumn.Description: Extracts the month out of the the Oder Date value from the Revenue Facts table. This information is extracted by BIEE server.

PresentationColumn.name: Billed Date
PresentationColumn.Description: Returns the Oder Bill Date value from the Revenue Facts table. This field is of type Date.

PresentationColumn.name: Billed Month
PresentationColumn.Description: Extracts the month out of the the Oder Bill Date value from the Revenue Facts table. This information is extracted by BIEE server.

PresentationColumn.name: Billed Year
PresentationColumn.Description: Extracts the year out of the the Oder Bill Date value from the Revenue Facts table. This information is extracted by BIEE server.
